{"tid":713424,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉]一人幾本細個好鍾意睇既書","createTime":"2018-06-22T19:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T02:16:51.000Z","uid":4876,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"7b642fd42d21fbfbdd5f544345c570a24ea034de","tid":713424,"uid":4876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T19:18:35.000Z","msg":"黑魔女學園<br />\n唔知有冇人睇過<br />\n小學個陣好鍾意睇<br />\n早排突然醒起上網SEARCH 原來連動畫都出左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n牛仔老夫子呢啲經典唔使講啦<br />\n仲有一本係本書入面夾住張膠卡<br />\n之後對應返書唔知邊一頁就會有啲資料顯示左出黎<br />\n以前都好多人鍾意睇 不過我冇睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小學個陣會經常行學校圖書館借好多書去睇<br />\n結果依家越大個越懶得睇書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860a8eab294250d8920a622301ad390fbfd66a76","tid":713424,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T19:23:26.000Z","msg":"mein kampf"},{"pid":"da81b25ce933cb827d541c13df5da96f6b7b0776","tid":713424,"uid":52984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T19:24:28.000Z","msg":"我的小雞雞"},{"pid":"8b15428107878205157fb191cb495f084b64da92","tid":713424,"uid":92042,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T19:58:27.000Z","msg":"老鼠記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b7299a0698a226696669b0c3b1b89823c9df0e","tid":713424,"uid":12185,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T21:03:22.000Z","msg":"丁丁歷險記<br />\n最近又搵返英文版黎睇發覺幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8e311f4ab430ca9ef7d02bbdb83f2099cf45e7","tid":713424,"uid":190443,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T21:05:36.000Z","msg":"Q版特工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"561bb1f1af9d72bb6b661e57b9d58c05ef89df83","tid":713424,"uid":65879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T21:16:28.000Z","msg":"安地查東的羅密歐與茱麗葉<br />\n講一對企鵝比人放左去北極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個系列都係由呢個setting出發<br />\n每本講動物嘅愛情故事 好感人<br />\n（又好薄 以前年年都搵佢做book report<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細個好易搵到啲鐘意嘅書<br />\n可能因為好多時間可以睇好多書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f7607183c46ba26933fa725d0d0c876086d797","tid":713424,"uid":65298,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T21:42:42.000Z","msg":"朱颜血 丹杏"},{"pid":"1e7cc44ebec6e74624e83d87054cf1ebdac76d0e","tid":713424,"uid":65298,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"c0f7607183c46ba26933fa725d0d0c876086d797","tid":713424,"uid":65298,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T21:42:42.000Z","msg":"朱颜血 丹杏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T21:43:39.000Z","msg":"顏 <br />\nsorry copy左殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acde8a31c9fa570fdfef40c6dc6f2f0261fbfd26","tid":713424,"uid":68083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T21:48:05.000Z","msg":"三毛<br />\n牛仔"},{"pid":"3f234942c3f3eeb5617ea38a0e0dc3d09372ce6b","tid":713424,"uid":4876,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T21:58:18.000Z","msg":"仲有一本漫畫<br />\n上年書展見到勁想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係講沙漠/無人島求生個啲<br />\n小學個陣本本追<br />\n有啲講尋寶既唔多好睇<br />\n求生個啲先好睇<br />\n中間會加插啲小知識<br />\n例如係沙漠點定位 係無人島點filter出乾淨水<br />\n作者好似真係實地去過先畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總之真係好好睇<