i\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n牛仔老夫子呢啲經典唔使講啦<br />\n仲有一本係本書入面夾住張膠卡<br />\n之後對應返書唔知邊一頁就會有啲資料顯示左出黎<br />\n以前都好多人鍾意睇 不過我冇睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小學個陣會經常行學校圖書館借好多書去睇<br />\n結果依家越大個越懶得睇書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T11:03:37.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣細個係公共圖書館行過見到第一集覺得幾得意就借左嚟睇<br />\n點知一睇上左癮<br />\n好似有10本up全部睇曬<br />\n就係E套書令我開始左中意睇小說<br />\n到而加仲會睇埋其他書<br />\n好慶幸個日有睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5391cf7e4f5868be30c80b885505a756be0558","tid":713424,"uid":147459,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:30:20.000Z","msg":"面書"},{"pid":"a6092452cb1c4885c6634ab37bfe05028edec828","tid":713424,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e7cc44ebec6e74624e83d87054cf1ebdac76d0e","tid":713424,"uid":65298,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"c0f7607183c46ba26933fa725d0d0c876086d797","tid":713424,"uid":65298,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T21:42:42.000Z","msg":"朱颜血 丹杏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T21:43:39.000Z","msg":"顏 <br />\nsorry copy左殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我中意佢前期作品武俠多啲"},{"pid":"fa678ad28a81cbbe12f19a99aa4b670b6d212eb7","tid":713424,"uid":54387,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1bba1629c78ffb52d07b550ed7c550c8ae6191f5","tid":713424,"uid":67325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T00:49:28.000Z","msg":"鬼屋之夜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:59:17.000Z","msg":"彗星來臨之夜<br />\n死亡請柬<br />\n金盒裡的一雙手<br />\n吸血鬼歸來<br />\n<br />\n可惜決擇叢書只得十本八本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63dc10bad91589a65b00364a97690cc36af0834d","tid":713424,"uid":130907,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:09:28.000Z","msg":"初中超迷天航系列<br />\n有三分神射手、愛情亞米巴系列<br />\n最鍾意書蟲的少年時代、披著狼皮的羊咩咩⋯⋯<br />\n寫得好有中學雞情懷，又搞笑！<br />\n<br />\n仲有鄭梓靈、張小嫻、林詠琛⋯⋯"},{"pid":"ce9cc29cd26bee2eded47797a8383bb6bd37cd9b","tid":713424,"uid":22409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:18:34.000Z","msg":"向達倫大冒險<br />\n人性的弱點"},{"pid":"d42c89625d34b80d0f63579d26b7e0c1b24d1e5b","tid":713424,"uid":14914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇過呢套<br />\n好似小三個陣，老師比左其中一本我地睇<br />\n係日本人寫嘅，啲情節勁無厘頭，但好搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一睇完就好中意，成套借哂黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/222912_dbbcb4e65410e6ab62f2c507b17cc78e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F222912_dbbcb4e65410e6ab62f2c507b17cc78e.png&h=40c5a5c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲記得個主角個花名係「十塊錢便宜貨」<br />\n太奇怪所以記到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b1a1359dca6c3e77e01a34baeafa56e3accf2e","tid":713424,"uid":4876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f5be7c9ac160e07903d82e6e1afe0dd23675ec4","tid":713424,"uid":15251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b642fd42d21fbfbdd5f544345c570a24ea034de","tid":713424,"uid":4876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T19:18:35.000Z","msg":"黑魔女學園<br />\n唔知有冇人睇過<br />\n小學個陣好鍾意睇<br />\n早排突然醒起上網SEARCH 原來連動畫都出左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n牛仔老夫子呢啲經典唔使講啦<br />\n仲有一本係本書入面夾住張膠卡<br />\n之後對應返書唔知邊一頁就會有啲資料顯示左出黎<br />\n以前都好多人鍾意睇 不過我冇睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小學個陣會經常行學校圖書館借好多書去睇<br />\n結果依家越大個越懶得睇書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T11:03:37.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣細個係公共圖書館行過見到第一集覺得幾得意就借左嚟睇<br />\n點知一睇上左癮<br />\n好似有10本up全部睇曬<br />\n就係E套書令我開始左中意睇小說<br />\n到而加仲會睇埋其他書<br />\n好慶幸個日有睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T15:04:35.000Z","msg":"個陣見本書封面好靚先開始睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依家一路睇動畫 啲記憶出返晒黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce599a75e49c6fd5868cf5f6832f1581035a2616","tid":713424,"uid":4876,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T15:06:31.000Z","msg":"講開漫畫<br />\n除左香港馬仔畫既低能系列之外<br />\n我以前都好鍾意睇日本高木直子畫既漫畫<br />\n第一次係睇呢本<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/230617_8efbd67139daca79763bc94bcbf6e69e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F230617_8efbd67139daca79763bc94bcbf6e69e.png&h=ece4b902&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8ad005bac5b52cc4e9e0dbd211d9a1a9fd51bea","tid":713424,"uid":4876,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"c5cf03e73dd99c21bb2b1e4c24e942f822063e05","tid":713424,"uid":191938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f234942c3f3eeb5617ea38a0e0dc3d09372ce6b","tid":713424,"uid":4876,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T21:58:18.000Z","msg":"仲有一本漫畫<br />\n上年書展見到勁想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係講沙漠/無人島求生個啲<br />\n小學個陣本本追<br />\n有啲講尋寶既唔多好睇<br />\n求生個啲先好睇<br />\n中間會加插啲小知識<br />\n例如係沙漠點定位 係無人島點filter出乾淨水<br />\n作者好似真係實地去過先畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總之真係好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:52:34.000Z","msg":"你講完我先諗番起細個好鐘意呢本書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T15:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/230911_88b0960c4f4fce260434293bd4f2dd20.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F230911_88b0960c4f4fce260434293bd4f2dd20.png&h=d424b570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成個系列都好睇又好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d918410d58d4289df67d91656186d02e33be93","tid":713424,"uid":11089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T15:18:52.000Z","msg":"一隻盧仔的回憶<br />\n個故事用第一人稱去講<br />\n好多內容都好深刻<br />\n仲記得係小學圖書館借嘅<br />\n唔知有冇人睇過呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a74293170ca59f9338f7ba77d1408c6f381825a","tid":713424,"uid":43751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T15:22:55.000Z","msg":"兒童周刊"},{"pid":"f11fd9046e449ab28e8cbf430ea9e7215d1321f1","tid":713424,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T15:24:41.000Z","msg":"快樂龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有一套用壽司做主角嘅漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3d6dd7638c3cc58025b672abca45e7bfa958cc","tid":713424,"uid":108006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi