lass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n牛仔老夫子呢啲經典唔使講啦<br />\n仲有一本係本書入面夾住張膠卡<br />\n之後對應返書唔知邊一頁就會有啲資料顯示左出黎<br />\n以前都好多人鍾意睇 不過我冇睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小學個陣會經常行學校圖書館借好多書去睇<br />\n結果依家越大個越懶得睇書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T19:13:09.000Z","msg":"哆啦A夢"},{"pid":"61ee8742fa4693120ecccf72fe58628dfa54fbfd","tid":713424,"uid":117631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da81b25ce933cb827d541c13df5da96f6b7b0776","tid":713424,"uid":52984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T19:24:28.000Z","msg":"我的小雞雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T19:13:41.000Z","msg":"呢本我都有睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a659f2c1793d3a43785fd890655d1265c0aa5d","tid":713424,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"561bb1f1af9d72bb6b661e57b9d58c05ef89df83","tid":713424,"uid":65879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T21:16:28.000Z","msg":"安地查東的羅密歐與茱麗葉<br />\n講一對企鵝比人放左去北極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個系列都係由呢個setting出發<br />\n每本講動物嘅愛情故事 好感人<br />\n（又好薄 以前年年都搵佢做book report<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細個好易搵到啲鐘意嘅書<br />\n可能因為好多時間可以睇好多書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T19:48:53.000Z","msg":"你講到好吸引 想即刻買本睇吓"},{"pid":"c935881d902fa37666e47bec6698b81d284453cd","tid":713424,"uid":88755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d42c89625d34b80d0f63579d26b7e0c1b24d1e5b","tid":713424,"uid":14914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇過呢套<br />\n好似小三個陣，老師比左其中一本我地睇<br />\n係日本人寫嘅，啲情節勁無厘頭，但好搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一睇完就好中意，成套借哂黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/222912_dbbcb4e65410e6ab62f2c507b17cc78e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F222912_dbbcb4e65410e6ab62f2c507b17cc78e.png&h=40c5a5c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲記得個主角個花名係「十塊錢便宜貨」<br />\n太奇怪所以記到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T20:01:51.000Z","msg":"小學圖書館有 好鍾意睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1849e2beb98234f6586109b78bb70b6c4a5c6c8a","tid":713424,"uid":88755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8ad005bac5b52cc4e9e0dbd211d9a1a9fd51bea","tid":713424,"uid":4876,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"c5cf03e73dd99c21bb2b1e4c24e942f822063e05","tid":713424,"uid":191938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f234942c3f3eeb5617ea38a0e0dc3d09372ce6b","tid":713424,"uid":4876,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T21:58:18.000Z","msg":"仲有一本漫畫<br />\n上年書展見到勁想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係講沙漠/無人島求生個啲<br />\n小學個陣本本追<br />\n有啲講尋寶既唔多好睇<br />\n求生個啲先好睇<br />\n中間會加插啲小知識<br />\n例如係沙漠點定位 係無人島點filter出乾淨水<br />\n作者好似真係實地去過先畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總之真係好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:52:34.000Z","msg":"你講完我先諗番起細個好鐘意呢本書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T15:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/230911_88b0960c4f4fce260434293bd4f2dd20.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservic